{"tid":286324,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣撚]咁既情況,應該住台北定宜蘭?","createTime":"2017-06-16T13:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T12:14:45.000Z","uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05791f5feea090176efc156a8a2774c493a68d31","tid":286324,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"話說上個月同屋企人第一次去台灣<br />\n個幾日都係台北<br />\n唔知係唔係因為酒店係中正區,試過一晚係個頭行過,感覺同香港差唔多,冇好多人講咁落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己係布袋戲撚<br />\n之前發現我睇開個檔布袋戲係宜蘭個國立傳統藝術中心開咗間傳藝店<br />\n但個幾日都冇去<br />\n諗住遲D 9 OR 10月再去過<br />\n到時一定去宜蘭間傳藝店<br />\n但依家有個問題<br />\n本身唔係太熟台灣D環境,聽人話宜蘭好似好落後好鄉下,交通更落後,我驚如果下次去直接住係宜蘭,自己會唔習慣個到D環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自問自己係典型都市人,如果住台北一定OK,但就怕去宜蘭要好Q耐,去一次都要成3個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既情況,到底我應該住台北定宜蘭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013e2b12ead1e70cd0bd84c8dc88c26999752d7a","tid":286324,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c66b8b3a689ade0b7dc193fcf8dfa053b5614ab","tid":286324,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"留係香港。 宜蘭差唔多第三世界咁款。你會生存唔到"},{"pid":"0a6b6273908af99278ff918f3e52aa0480d04ab6","tid":286324,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留係香港。 宜蘭差唔多第三世界咁款。你會生存唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83197efb17010082238b8596