" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未入隧道已經比人截住啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0d743aec90495fd88a0b7986bd31bc7f958fb8","tid":286324,"uid":76683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"你有無睇過布袋戲傳藝店嘅相?<br />\n睇完嘅可以唔使去,我覺得無乜野睇,<br />\n得金光十零個原版公仔係度,除非你係金光死忠,<br />\n入去瘋狂買野,你當佢純粹賣野嘅鋪頭會無咁嬲,<br />\n如果想了解布袋戲文化,去錯地方"},{"pid":"a21a4703ae051edcca53a7fd247ca50ca2ff98c3","tid":286324,"uid":71736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"宜蘭堅係鄉下地區<br />\n住台北，stay 兩日一夜宜蘭囉"},{"pid":"2f9cc570363c8eef68fa92cc440ca145f9c66650","tid":286324,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有無睇過布袋戲傳藝店嘅相?<br />\n睇完嘅可以唔使去,我覺得無乜野睇,<br />\n得金光十零個原版公仔係度,除非你係金光死忠,<br />\n入去瘋狂買野,你當佢純粹賣野嘅鋪頭會無咁嬲,<br />\n如果想了解布袋戲文化,去錯地方</blockquote><br />\n你都係金光撚??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177707bfe506e34fbadb1df998eed939b376a5f9","tid":286324,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係烈空龍巴打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8703c31b07719a0bd0819a1f43b65b8f65f919da","tid":286324,"uid":76683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你有無睇過布袋戲傳藝店嘅相?<br />\n睇完嘅可以唔使去,我覺得無乜野睇,<br />\n得金光十零個原版公仔係度,除非你係金光死忠,<br />\n入去瘋狂買野,你當佢純粹賣野嘅鋪頭會無咁嬲,<br />\n如果想了解布袋戲文化,去錯地方</blockquote><br />\n你都係金光撚??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係, 我淨係睇過史豔文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次台灣fd帶去宜蘭,順路見到,  <br />\n不過果間鋪無冷氣, 熱撚死人<br />\nbtw宜蘭好山好水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n不過你無車係可以收皮,<br />\nd景點隔得好遠, 而且真係鄉下地方"},{"pid":"34980f5125b785dd66ebc8f813ed7c14d62ca360","tid":286324,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你有無睇過布袋戲傳藝店嘅相?<br />\n睇完嘅可以唔使去,我覺得無乜野睇,<br />\n得金光十零個原版公仔係度,除非你係金光死忠,<br />\n入去瘋狂買野,你當佢純粹賣野嘅鋪頭會無咁嬲,<br />\n如果想了解布袋戲文化,去錯地方</blockquote><br />\n你都係金光撚??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係, 我淨係睇過史豔文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次台灣fd帶去宜蘭,順路見到,  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過果間鋪無冷氣, 熱撚死人</span><br />\nbtw宜蘭好山好水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n不過你無車係可以收皮,<br />\nd景點隔得好遠, 而且真係鄉下地方</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/46648_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F46648_WM.jpg&h=8c2567d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7a112b2352699704eb29bab3b6b80b69cccaa93","tid":286324,"uid":69049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"早兩日去完宜蘭返 日日都落大雨<br />\n啲鋪頭好多唔開 無車要行好遠(就算食野都係)<br />\n有開既鋪頭大部分都無冷氣<br />\n係礁溪住咗一晚溫泉旅館 夜晚去羅東夜市行下食下<br />\n玩一晚浸下溫泉都ok既"}]}